        <h2>Horizontal Alignment</h2>
        <p>
            Horizontal alignment classes are applied to flex parents.
            Left alignment is the default, but you can use one of these classes to change this:
            <Code Content="YWxpZ24tcmlnaHQ="></Code>, <Code Content="YWxpZ24tY2VudGVy"></Code>, <Code Content="YWxpZ24tanVzdGlmeQ=="></Code>, <Code Content="YWxpZ24tc3BhY2Vk"></Code>
        </p>
